# SpecKit installation and generated files
# These directories are auto-generated and should not be committed

# .speckit/ - SpecKit CLI installation
# Regenerated automatically on first run or update
.speckit/

# .specify/ - SpecKit project templates and configuration
# Regenerated during initialization
.specify/

# Claude Code local settings (may contain credentials)
# Keep .claude/commands/ tracked - those are the SpecKit workflow commands
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/settings.json
.claude/credentials*
.claude/*.key

# Wireframe backup files (created during regeneration)
*.reference.svg

# Wireframe viewer test artifacts
docs/design/wireframes/node_modules/
docs/design/wireframes/package-lock.json
docs/design/wireframes/playwright-report/
docs/design/wireframes/screenshots/
.env
